Reports references inside the following Spring Data JDBC annotations if they cannot be resolved within the configured datasource:<br/>
<ul>
  <li> @Table(name, schema)</li>
  <li> @Column(name)</li>
  <li> @MappedCollection(idColumn, keyColumn)</li>
</ul><br/>

<!-- tooltip end -->
<p>
  <b>NOTE:</b> Datasource can be configured via `Assign datasource` action or the corresponding gutter icon for entity class
</p>
